<title>ITALY: TABLE - ITALY JUNE PRODUCER PRICES ROSE 1.6 PCT.</title>
<headline>TABLE - ITALY JUNE PRODUCER PRICES ROSE 1.6 PCT.</headline>
<dateline>ROME 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>National statistics office ISTAT gave the following Italian producer price data for June.</p>
<p>    PRODUCER PRICES	     June 97  May 97	June 96</p>
<p>    Year/year change	   +1.6 pct +1.1 pct     +0.6 pct</p>
<p>    Month/month change	 +0.1 pct +0.1 pct     -0.2 pct</p>
<p>    Index (base 1995=100)     103.1    103.0	  124.0</p>
<p>Istat gave the following general breakdown:</p>
<p>				  Mo/Mo change (%)    Yr/Yr change (%)</p>
<p>    Consumer goods	   0.0		    +0.7</p>
<p>    Investment goods	+0.1		    +1.8</p>
<p>    Intermediate goods    +0.1		    +2.2</p>
<p>It gave the following sector-by-sector breakdown:</p>
<p>    Sector			    mo/mo (%)	     yr/yr (%)</p>
<p>    Minerals			  +1.0		    +6.5</p>
<p>    Non-metal minerals	     0.0		    +3.8</p>
<p>    Chemicals			 -0.1		    +2.1</p>
<p>    Metal works		     +0.3		    +0.2</p>
<p>    Cars and parts		  -0.6		    -0.8</p>
<p>    Food, drink and tobacco     +0.1		    +0.3</p>
<p>    Clothing and textiles	 +0.4		    +1.0</p>
<p>    Leather goods		   +0.1		    +1.6</p>
<p>    Energy products		 +0.1		    +7.9</p>
<p>-- Rome newsroom +396 678 2501</p>
